description: The status of the booking in the process. Possible values are - RECE (Received) - PENU (Pending Update) - DRAFT (Draft) - PENA (Pending Approval) - APPR (Approved) - ISSU (Issued) - SURR (Surrendered) - VOID (Void) More details can be found on GitHub. Be aware that the list provided here is a subset of the possible values.
